testCodes.label: Lyme Exposure
testCodes.description: Contrary to what the name implies, lyme disease is not a disease, but rather a sign of exposure to the bacteria borrelia.  This bacteria is not contagious, and cannot be spread to humans or other animals.

testCodes.label: Ehrlichia Exposure
testCodes.description: Fido is not contagious and cannot spread this infection to any dogs or people.
